rnal/biz/wapi/mixing.go:58`\n  - `internal/biz/wapi/market.go:46`\n  - `internal
/biz/wcity/wcc/building_map.go:105`\n  - `internal/biz/wmix/mixing.go:51`\n- **
描述**: `MixingUseCase`、`MarketUseCase`、`BuildingMap` 等 Biz 层结构体在构造函
数内部直接调用 `eventbus.NewEventAdapter("api")`、`NewEventAdapter("city")` 等硬
